OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather cloudy start to the
OL,6,Fday, but blue skies returning through
OL,7,Fthe morning as the cloud clears away.
OL,8,FA hot afternoon to come, with light
OL,9,Fwinds across the region and plenty of
OL,10,Fhazy sunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FPlenty of sunshine to end the
OL,13,Fday. Dry overnight, with increasing
OL,14,Famounts of cloud cover once more,
OL,15,Fthough southern and western areas
OL,16,Fholding on to some clearer skies.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
